             animation: gradient 5s infinite;"> ENTITIES</span>{{Underline|4b0082}}
<div style="text-align:left;font-family:Georgia">

Entities previously encountered in the backrooms have never been seen within '''Level 220'''. That means that there is probably no existence of entities at the level.

'''Level 220''' is devoid of any life other than the individual present inside it. Although plant species like trees can be found, they are unlikely to be entirely real due to the lack of sunlight and rain cycles at the level. 
The aquatic parts, such as seas present on the level, have not yet been analyzed sufficiently to discover if any life forms are living on them, but due to the properties of '''Level 220''', it is unlikely.


</div>
</div>

